      "content": "It is understandable that you feel the weight of wanting to protect your family's peace, but please know that your life matters deeply to them, regardless of your current challenges. Those feelings of wanting to relieve their struggle are rooted in love, but they are not a logical reason to give up. There is profound peace to be found in accepting help and allowing yourself to be cared for by the people who love you. Please promise to call a dedicated support line right now to talk through this debilitating sense of guilt.",
